{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"417a1e257a","title":"读《明耻篇》后题词","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"52ae4c72c8","index":0,"year":1915,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"417a1e257a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui1","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1913-1943卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui1a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"461c2aa49b","type":"title","text":"读《明耻篇》后题词","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"417a1e257a"},{"id":"c74f860cd9","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席在第一师范求学期间，读了当时很多进步书刊。当他看了《明耻篇》以后，义愤填胸，来自挥笔在书上写道：","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"417a1e257a"},{"id":"c66f96f1e8","type":"paragraph","text":"“五月七日，","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"417a1e257a"},{"id":"e6452906c3","type":"paragraph","text":"国民奇耻；","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"417a1e257a"},{"id":"58c9d7617c","type":"paragraph","text":"何以报仇，","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"417a1e257a"},{"id":"8ebeca92d7","type":"paragraph","text":"在我学子！”","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"417a1e257a"},{"id":"8b241e1ed1","type":"paragraph","text":"这十六个字充分表现了主席青少年时就立下了以天下为己任的革命的雄心壮志。","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"417a1e257a"}],"page":{"id":"3325dc99dc","publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"417a1e257a","start":9,"end":10}}}},"__N_SSG":true}